INPUT
--> [Multiplier
      gain: dB 5
    ]
--> [Delayer
      delay: 400
      mix: %% 3333
    ]
--> [LowPass
      high_cut: % 2
    ]
--> [MidScooper
      low_cut: % 1
      high_cut: % 3
    ]
--> [Compressor
      ratio: 2
      threshold: dB -10
      attack: % 5
      mix: % 70
    ]
--> OUTPUT

Simple warm tone simulator.
